<form
  class="{{cssClass}} {{actor.type}} overflow-auto bg-white font-serif"
  autocomplete="off"
>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl p-6">
    <div class="border-4 border-double border-black">
      <h1
        class="my-1 translate-y-px text-center font-serif text-4xl font-bold"
        style="font-variant-caps: small-caps;"
      >Kale Arkham</h1>
      <p class="m-0 mb-2 text-center font-serif italic">A burglar and petty
        sorcerer, first mate and mechanic of The Owl</p>

      <div class="mb-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2">
        <!-- Traits & Tags -->
        <div class="md:col-span-2">
          <div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center bg-black">
            <h2
              class="m-0 translate-y-px py-0.5 text-center font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-white uppercase"
            >Traits & Tags</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 border-y md:grid-cols-4">
            <div class="border-x">
              <div class="border-b px-4 py-2">
                <h4 class="m-0 font-serif text-xl font-normal">Burglar</h4>
              </div>
              <div class="px-4 py-2">
                <p class="italic">Quiet</p>
                <p class="italic">Sneak</p>
                <p class="italic">Dexterous</p>
                <p class="italic">Locks</p>
                <p class="italic">Perceptive</p>
                <p class="italic">Traps</p>
                <p class="italic">Darkness</p>
                <p class="italic">Alarm</p>
                <p class="italic">Distractions</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Keys -->
        <div class="border-r-1 border-black">
          <div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center bg-black">
            <h2
              class="m-0 translate-y-px py-0.5 text-center font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-white uppercase"
            >Keys</h2>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-4 px-4 py-4">
            <div class="key">
              <div class="mb-2 overflow-hidden">
                <div class="relative border-2 border-black">
                  <i
                    class="absolute top-0 left-0 -mt-2 -ml-2 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-white"
                  ></i>
                  <i
                    class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mt-2 -mr-2 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-white"
                  ></i>
                  <p class="px-3 text-lg leading-4 font-semibold">Key of Greed</p>
                  <i
                    class="absolute right-0 bottom-0 -mr-2 -mb-2 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-white"
                  ></i>
                  <i
                    class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 -mb-2 -ml-2 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-white"
                  ></i>
                </div>
              </div>

              <p class="m-0">You like the shiny things. Turn this key when you
                steal something cool or score a big payoff.</p>
              <p class="m-0 italic">Buyoff: Swear off stealing forever.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="key">
              <div class="mb-2 overflow-hidden">
                <div class="relative border-2 border-black">
                  <i
                    class="absolute top-0 left-0 -mt-2 -ml-2 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-white"
                  ></i>
                  <i
                    class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mt-2 -mr-2 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-white"
                  ></i>
                  <p class="px-3 text-lg leading-4 font-semibold">Key of the
                    Mission</p>
                  <i
                    class="absolute right-0 bottom-0 -mr-2 -mb-2 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-white"
                  ></i>
                  <i
                    class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 -mb-2 -ml-2 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-white"
                  ></i>
                </div>
              </div>

              <p class="m-0">You must safely deliver Lady Blackbird to the
                Pirate King Uriah Flint, so she can marry him. Turn this key
                when you take action to complete the mission.</p>
              <p class="m-0 italic">Buyoff: Give up the mission.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="key">
              <div class="mb-2 overflow-hidden">
                <div class="relative border-2 border-black">
                  <i
                    class="absolute top-0 left-0 -mt-2 -ml-2 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-white"
                  ></i>
                  <i
                    class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mt-2 -mr-2 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-white"
                  ></i>
                  <p class="px-3 text-lg leading-4 font-semibold">Key of
                    Fraternity</p>
                  <i
                    class="absolute right-0 bottom-0 -mr-2 -mb-2 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-white"
                  ></i>
                  <i
                    class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 -mb-2 -ml-2 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-white"
                  ></i>
                </div>
              </div>

              <p class="m-0">You are sworn to Captain Vance in a bond of
                brotherhood. Turn this key when your character is influenced by
                Vance or when you show how deep your bond is.</p>
              <p class="m-0 italic">Buyoff: Sever the relationship.</p>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Secrets -->
        <div>
          <div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center bg-black">
            <h2
              class="m-0 translate-y-px py-0.5 text-center font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-white uppercase"
            >Secrets</h2>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-4 px-4 py-4">
            <div class="key">
              <div class="mb-2 overflow-hidden">
                <div class="relative border-2 border-black">
                  <i
                    class="absolute top-0 left-0 -mt-2 -ml-2 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-white"
                  ></i>
                  <i
                    class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mt-2 -mr-2 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-white"
                  ></i>
                  <p class="px-3 text-lg leading-4 font-semibold">Secret of
                    Concealment</p>
                  <i
                    class="absolute right-0 bottom-0 -mr-2 -mb-2 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-white"
                  ></i>
                  <i
                    class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 -mb-2 -ml-2 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-white"
                  ></i>
                </div>
              </div>

              <p class="m-0">No matter how thoroughly you're searched, you
                always have a few key items with you. You can produce any
                common, simple item at a moment's notice.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="key">
              <div class="mb-2 overflow-hidden">
                <div class="relative border-2 border-black">
                  <i
                    class="absolute top-0 left-0 -mt-2 -ml-2 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-white"
                  ></i>
                  <i
                    class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mt-2 -mr-2 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-white"
                  ></i>
                  <p class="px-3 text-lg leading-4 font-semibold">Secret of
                    Reflexes</p>
                  <i
                    class="absolute right-0 bottom-0 -mr-2 -mb-2 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-white"
                  ></i>
                  <i
                    class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 -mb-2 -ml-2 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-white"
                  ></i>
                </div>
              </div>

              <p class="m-0">Once per refresh, you can re-roll a failure when
                doing anything involving grace, dexterity, or quick reflexes.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Conditions, Pool, Items -->
      <div class="mb-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">Conditions</h2>
          <ul class="list-inside list-disc space-y-1 text-sm">
            <li>Injured</li>
            <li>Dead (presumed)</li>
            <li>Tired</li>
            <li>Angry</li>
            <li>Lost</li>
            <li>Hunted</li>
            <li>Trapped</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">Pool</h2>
          <p class="text-sm">Maximum: ●●●●●●●</p>
          <p class="text-sm">Current: ●●●●●●●</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">Items & Appearance</h2>
          <p class="mb-1 text-sm">Kale Arkham begins detained in the brig,
            weaponless.</p>
          <p class="text-sm">Items: Mechanic's garb and tools — Dagger — Lock
            picks — Trick cards — Goggles</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- XP -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">XP</h2>
        <p class="mb-1 text-sm">Spend XP at any time to:</p>
        <ul class="list-inside list-disc space-y-1 text-sm">
          <li>5 XP — Add a new trait with 1–3 tags.</li>
          <li>5 XP — Add a new key you’ve never had before.</li>
          <li>5 XP — Add a new secret.</li>
          <li>5 XP — Increase pool maximum by 1 (and get a pool die).</li>
          <li>3 XP — Unlock a tag on an existing trait.</li>
          <li>1 XP — Get a pool die (up to your pool maximum).</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</form>